Interface ProcessManager<R>

  • Type Parameters:
    R - Type of task to be run.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LongRunningProcessManager, NativeProcessManager, ProcessManagerWrapper, TensorFlowServerManager

    public interface ProcessManager<R>
    Process manager that allows to run and maintain processes in the cluster.
